crosoft YaHei\'; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); overflow: hidden; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/232151515du5.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"WB_text\" node-type=\"feed_list_reason\" style=\"padding-bottom: 3px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/23px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); overflow: hidden; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23215205vkic.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"WB_text\" node-type=\"feed_list_reason\" style=\"padding-bottom: 3px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/23px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); overflow: hidden; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23215220u91w.jpg\" /></div>\r\n', '/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23215220u91w.jpg', '1', '1', '2015-07-29 21:24:00', '国网北京电力', '2015-08-14 13:59:06', '[图片]', '0', '2', '');
INSERT INTO `jc_microblog` VALUES ('10', '好样的，“蜘蛛人”！', '', '<div class=\"WB_info\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 3px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 5px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">@国网北京石景山供电公司</div>\r\n<div class=\"WB_text\" node-type=\"feed_list_reason\" style=\"padding-bottom: 3px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/23px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); overflow: hidden; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">大雨过后的&ldquo;桑拿天&rdquo;里，石景山区广宁路上出现了一群&ldquo;蜘蛛人&rdquo;，他们爬到电杆上为电网&ldquo;诊脉&rdquo;，将老旧设备换掉，优化网架结构，增强电力设备的健康水平，有效的提高了供电能力，让我们踏实的度过炎热的夏天~@国网北京市电力公司@亮报<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>@国家电网报<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>@国家电网杂志</div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/2321583556z7.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23215848k08i.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23215908paxo.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23215928cvtf.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23215952gm3q.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23220022uqwh.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '', '1', '1', '2015-07-29 21:25:00', '国网北京电力', '2015-08-14 13:59:28', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jc_microblog` VALUES ('11', '“掌上电力”APP，不只在家买电这么简单', '', '<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold\">（一）<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">什</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">么是&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;AP</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">P？</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP是国家电网公司推出了一个官方手机客户端，主要提供居民用电相关服务，可实现客户<span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">7&times;24小时用电查询、交费购电、信息订阅、在线客服、网点导航、停电公告、知识查阅</span>等服务功能。</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold\">（二）</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold\">除了上述基础服务，&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP还有哪些特色服务？</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">1.&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP支持一个注册用户绑定5个家庭用户编号。通过该功能，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">用户可绑定其父母或直系亲属的用户编号，实现家庭用电数据的集中管理。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2.&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;还<span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">支持代他人及异地交费</span>。客户输入要代为交费的用电客户编号、要交纳的金额即可为其他人代为交费。同时，客户通过手机客户端还可以<span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">实现跨省交费功能</span>，仅需切换到相应地区，注册为当地手机客户端用户即可实现交费。</div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23220842sqay.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold\">（三）通过哪些渠道可以下载安装&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP？</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP目前支持IOS、Android两种主流手机操作系统。IOS版手机客户可通过App&nbsp;Store下载使用，Android版手机客户可通过91手机助手、豌豆荚、360手机助手、应用汇、应用宝、小米应用商店、百度手机助手、安卓市场等应用商店下载使用。</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold\">（四）&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP怎么查查用电量电费信息和电费余额？ &nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">打开&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP，点击&ldquo;我的用电&rdquo;菜单中的&ldquo;用电查询&rdquo;子菜单中的&ldquo;电量电费&rdquo;功能，您可以查看近三年的年度总电量电费、月度电量电费。阶梯电价用电客户还可以查看您用电所处的阶梯档。</div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23220940w8sm.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">点击&ldquo;用电查询&rdquo;子菜单中的&ldquo;电费余额&rdquo;功能，后付费客户可查询账户余额情况，预付费智能表、城区煤改电网络表客户可查询最近日期零点采集的电表内余额。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold\">（五）</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">用&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP怎么买电？</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">打开&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP，点击&ldquo;我的用电&rdquo;菜单中的&ldquo;支付购电&rdquo;功能。先指定交费购电客户，可为已开通用电服务客户交费购电，也可为他人代交电费。</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">然后，选择支付方式，确定交费购电金额。</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">最后，进入银联支付平台，输入已开通银联在线支付的银联卡卡号等信息，完成资金支付。</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/26px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23221122w3h1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n', '/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201601/23221122w3h1.jpg', '1', '1', '2015-07-29 10:38:00', '国网北京电力', '2015-08-14 13:59:41', '[图片]', '0', '3', '');
INSERT INTO `jc_microblog` VALUES ('12', '【用“掌上电力”APP怎么买电？】', '', '<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/23px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">【用&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP怎么买电？】 打开&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP，点击&ldquo;我的用电&rdquo;菜单中的&ldquo;支付购电&rdquo;功能。先指定交费购电客户，可为已开通用电服务客户交费购电，也可为他人代交。然后，选择支付方式，确定交费购电金额。最后，进入银联支付平台，输入已开通银联在线支付的银联卡卡号等信息，完成支付。</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"WB_info\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 3px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 5px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">@亮报</div>\r\n<div class=\"WB_text\" node-type=\"feed_list_reason\" style=\"padding-bottom: 3px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/23px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); overflow: hidden; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">【&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP，这样买电更方便！】我发表了文章<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a action-type=\"feed_list_url\" class=\"W_btn_b btn_22px W_btn_cardlink\" href=\"/Jeedw/zhuzhan//20160123/140.html\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(217,217,217) 1px solid; min-width: 28px; text-align: left; border-left: rgb(217,217,217) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); margin: 0px 2px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; padding-left: 5px; outline-width: medium; padding-right: 5px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; height: 20px; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12px; vertical-align: middle; border-top: rgb(217,217,217) 1px s