"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">、影响力之服务首都</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14pt/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;服务京津冀协同发展，正在建设锡盟-北京东-山东、蒙西-北京西-天津南两条特高压工程。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16pt\">全部建成后北京电网外受电能力将在原有的基础上增加近一倍</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201510/311527199zb2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; display: inline !important; font: 19.09px/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; font: 14pt/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">计划用3-4年时间，建成与北京城市地位相适应的国际一流智能配电网。预计2017年，北京重点区域年户均停电时间35分钟以内。</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201510/31152759tr0h.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; display: inline !important; font: 19.09px/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">实施煤改电工程，积极建设电动汽车充换电服务设施，推行&ldquo;电能替代&rdquo;战略，服务清洁空气行动计划。</span></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201510/31152826fbfl.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 19.09px/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold\">4<span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">、影响力之情系百姓</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 19.09px/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14pt\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">&nbsp;首都电力共产党员服务队践行党的群众路线，打通电力服务&ldquo;最后一公里&rdquo;。</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201510/31152859wgml.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; display: inline !important; font: 19.09px/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">推广智能电表，市民可通过手机客户端、微信、支付宝、电费充值卡等方式购电，&ldquo;足不出户&rdquo;享受&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;服务。</span></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201510/31152928h66l.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; display: inline !important; font: 19.09px/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; font: 14pt/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">暴雨、暴雪容易引发电力故障导致停电。不要担心，电力工人就在风雨兼程，赶往抢修的路上！</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201510/311529546k59.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201510/31153108ptum.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; display: inline !important; font: 19.09px/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 37.33px; font: 14pt/30.9px 仿宋_GB2312; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 