运行功率，机顶盒待机一天耗电0.36度，一个月10.8度，一年129.6度。不算不知道。一算要关掉。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,176,240); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">节电窍门儿</strong></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,176,240); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(248,247,245); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 强烈建议您用遥控器关闭后，在断开电源，以防小钱钱，不是，是电量白白流失。</span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">耗电榜第四名 冰箱</span></span></div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/050938362lx6.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">体型和耗电量不成正比，它为&ldquo;箱&rdquo;忠厚，是一个可以交的朋友。它待机保温功率很小，制冷启动后功率较大65-100</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">瓦</span></span><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">，1小时耗电0.065-0.1度。冰箱24小时常开，但制冷压缩机不会持续运行，实际并不费电，可以放心使用。虽然电冰箱不太费电，但我们还是有更节能的使用方式哦。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,176,240); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">节电窍门儿</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,176,240); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(248,247,245); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 建议选用国家标准的节能冰箱（只买对的，不买贵的），并将其放在离热源远一点的地方,不要长时间打开冰箱门,不要将物品堆得太满、太密。此外,还要进行及时除霜,冷冻室霜层达4―6毫米,制冷时将比正常制冷多消耗1/3的电量。</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">耗电榜第五名 无线路由器</span></div>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(91,155,213); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">没有路由器的世界，我不敢想象，大家和小编一样吧，这个必须有。和它的作用相比，它在耗电&ldquo;琅琊榜&rdquo;排名几乎不值一提。无线路由器的运行功率在1.5-4</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">瓦</span><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/25px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">，一天的耗电量为0.036度-0.096度。无线路由器的耗电量很小，亲们，尽情的刷屏吧！</span></span><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Ar