size: auto; background-clip: border-box; background-origin: padding-box\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">2.</span></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(135,201,67); background-attachment: scroll; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-position: 0% 0%; color: white; background-size: auto; background-clip: border-box; background-origin: padding-box\">拿到《新能源小客车购车充电条件确认书》（格式如下）</span></span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-position: 0% 0%; height: auto !important; padding-top: 0px; background-size: auto; background-clip: border-box; background-origin: padding-box\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\"background-color: white; background-attachment: scroll; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-position: 0% 0%; color: rgb(135,201,67); font-size: 12pt; background-size: auto; background-clip: border-box; background-origin: padding-box\">▲</span><span style=\"background-color: white; background-attachment: scroll; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-position: 0% 0%; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 12pt; background-size: auto; background-clip: border-box; background-origin: padding-box\">满足上述条件，到您所在区县的供电营业厅，就可以提出用电申请了。</span></span></p>\r\n	<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/07104742x9df.jpg\" /></p>\r\n	<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214,0,74); background-att