\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/24px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(71,193,168); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 20px/28px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(255,255,255); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63,63,63); font-size: 16px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63,63,63); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">达尔问环境研究所的赫晓霞博士曾对西城区鸦儿胡同等</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63,63,63); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">8</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63,63,63); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">条胡同的煤改电配套设施进行电磁场</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.5em \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/10134148a90e.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.5em \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-align: left; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(63,63,63); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">测试发现，虽然煤改电设备晚上用电量比白天要高，但最高值仍远低于国家安全标准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.5em \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/101342193qcg.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"text-align: left; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(63,63,63); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(63,63,63); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">此外，赫晓霞称，从测试结果看，煤改电设备的电磁场处在一个相对较低的水平，与一般家用电器电磁场水平相似，正常使用的情况下不会对人体健康造成损害。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"text-align: left; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(63,63,63); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(63,63,63); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.4em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(71,193,168); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(68,114,196); font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">2、农村地区电价补贴，如何执行？</span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.5em \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"text-align: left; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(63,63,63); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/26px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(63,63,63); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63,63,63); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 根据《关于完善北京农村地区&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;&ldquo;煤改气&rdquo;相关政策的意见》，从2015年开始，</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63,63,63); padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; padding-top: