d-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2003年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-top: 0px\">完成第一批9000户居民电采暖示范改造。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2007年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-top: 0px\">&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;成为北京市&ldquo;治理大气污染，为绿色奥运做贡献&rdquo;的重点项目。西城、东城2万余户平房居民新增用电设备容量14万千瓦，每户6千瓦。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2009年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-top: 0px\">核心区、文保区&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;工程于当年采暖季前全面完成，涉及18万户平房居民。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2012年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-top: 0px\">&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;工程由首都核心区文保区向非文保区推进。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2013年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-top: 0px\">&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;工程继续发力，首都核心区最后一批4.4万户平房居民在采暖季用上电采暖。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2014年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-top: 0px\">按照市政府要求，将核心区未按计划拆迁居民和部分具备改造条件的简易楼居民纳入&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;施工范畴。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2015年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-top: 0px\">核心区&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;全面收尾，农村&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;迈入第三年，又将有5万农村居民享受到&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;的实惠。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,176,80); padding-top: 0px\">关注&ldquo;煤改电&rdquo;，</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,176,80); font-size: 20px; padding-top: 0px\">绿色清洁就在你身边！</span></strong></span></p>\r\n', '/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/10134336c3pi.jpg', '1', '1', '2015-11-10 13:44:03', '国网北京电力', '2015-11-10 13:44:03', '[图片]', '0', '1', '');
