INSERT INTO `jc_microblog` VALUES ('175', '冬季安全用电，您了解这些吗？', '', '<p><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">11月8日，立冬，农历二十四节气中的第十九个，&ldquo;立，建始也；冬，终也，万物收藏也。&rdquo;它代表冬季正式开始，也含有万物收藏、归避寒冷的意思。立冬过后，天气逐渐变冷，提醒您注意添衣防寒。 关于冬天，除了御寒外，我们还准备了一本&ldquo;冬季安全用电秘籍&rdquo;，陪伴您度过一个安全暖和的冬天。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 现在，就让咱来打开这本秘籍，看看到底说了啥！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">秘籍之一：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important\">选正规电器按规程操作</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 采购具有</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">3C</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">认证标志的用电设备。使用前要充分了解设备原理，严格按照说明书中的操作规程操作。过期、超期设备要及时淘汰。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/10140816h2y1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">秘籍之二：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">设备插座专插专用</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不要在一个插座上安插过多的插头，空调、电暖器等大功率设备最好享受</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">专插专用</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">的待遇，以免发生断电和其他意外</span>&nbsp;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/10140848pd9c.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">秘籍之三：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">用完电器断电源</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 电视、电脑、空调、电暖热备使用完后，要及时拔出电源插头。处于待机状态的家用电器不仅耗电，长期如此还可能引起火灾，存在安全风险。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/10140906xj54.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">秘籍之四：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">用电设施严禁沾水</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 洗衣机、电吹风、吸尘器等容易沾水潮湿的用电设施，使用时应严禁沾水。沐浴后，浴室内水蒸气较多，要定期检查浴室内开关、插座的安全防护，避免在潮湿环境中发生漏电。虽然现在大多数浴霸都防水，但使用时也不要将水溅到浴霸上，避免发生电源短路等危险。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/101410346ndl.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">秘籍之五：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">通电时间不宜长</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 电热毯通电时间不宜过长，一般在睡前</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">小时左右通电加热，尽量不要通宵使用。冬季空调长期运行会出现电器过热现象，建议每隔几个小时就关闭一次，并及时开窗通气。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/10141056gmuv.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">秘籍之六：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">取暖设备专物专用</span>&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 取暖器在使用时会产生高温，要与窗帘等易燃物保持一定距离，取暖设备要专物专用，不要利用这些电器来烘干潮湿的衣物。使用电磁炉、电热水器、热得快等电器时，应有人照看，防止干烧。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/101417272fng.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: bold\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold\">秘籍之七：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">有问题勿擅自处理</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 使用中的用电设备，出现糊味、焦味，应立即切断电源，并及时通知专业维修人员，不要擅自处理。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/10141746fucf.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/23.63px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 10.5pt/23.63px \'Times New Roman\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span 