INSERT INTO `jc_microblog` VALUES ('178', '停电了，请先做这些', '', '<p><span style=\"text-align: center; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14pt/27.27px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(255,0,255); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">对于现在无时无刻不刷屏的盆友们来说，最可怕的是</span><span style=\"text-align: center; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14pt/27.27px 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(255,0,255); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">：</span></p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/101444213yn1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/27.27px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;然而，停电后，很多亲打电话报修，却被接线的美眉问了又问。因为报修的停电情况有可能是自家的电器、电路等设备造成的，此部分故障可通过物业等途径找</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">有相关资质的电工</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt\">施工检查。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/27.27px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt\">了解了这些之后，停电报修前先进行自我检查，说不定自己就能解决了！&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/27.27px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt\">◆首先，询问邻居是否有电，若都无电，请拨打抢修电话：95598</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/27.27px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt\">◆&nbsp;如果只是自己家停电，那么请按照下列方法进行&ldquo;自我检查&rdquo;：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/27.27px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">1.检查自家电能表后的漏电保护器是否已跳开，或闸刀熔丝、保险盒熔丝是否熔断。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/27.27px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">2.若漏电保护器已跳开，在家中无人操作电器的情况下，可以试合漏电保护器，如果合不上，说明家中有故障，应请有相关资质的电工全面检查，消除故障后再送电。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13.63px/27.27px Arial, \'Microsoft YaHei\'; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: auto !important; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">3.若熔丝熔断，说明家中用电超负荷或有故障，应请有相关资质的电工全面检查，消除故障后再送电。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0pt 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">如上述检查正常完好，则可能是其他原因，请拨打抢修电话：</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">95598</span></span></p>\r\n', '/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201511/101444213yn1.jpg', '1', '1', '2015-11-10 14:44:38', '国网北京电力', '2015-11-10 14:44:38', '[图片]', '0', '1', '');
