INSERT INTO `jc_microblog` VALUES ('271', '【掌上电力，开通就有奖（第二季）】', '', '<p>掌上电力，开通有奖第一期已圆满结束，为回馈北京地区广大电力客户的支持，第二期有奖开通活动接踵而来，20万张5元电费充值卡，先到先得！</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 活动规则：2015年12月5日起北京地区用电客户在&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;手机客户端首次开通用电服务（每个注册账号可开通5个客户编号），每开通1个客户编号赠送5元电费充值卡，共20万张电费充值卡，先到先得，送完为止。</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 面向对象：在&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;App新注册账号并新开通的客户、已注册账号未开通满5个客户编号的客户。</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不属于有奖的范围：12月5日前已被绑定过的客户编号即使解绑后，重新绑定不做奖励；授权账号开通不做奖励。</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如何获得电费充值卡，电力超人来帮你！</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n	<p style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201602/02092925lv22.jpg\" /></p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">指尖轻轻一划，服务在您身边。今天，小编带大家认识一款居家必备神器</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(184,204,228); margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP</span>，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">这可是全国电力行业中的首个电力服务类APP。有了这一&ldquo;神器&rdquo;，您就可以足不出户，动动手指，轻松购电，省去了往返营业厅、排队等候等麻烦，还能快速进行用电查询，享受更多的电力服务。</span></span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">随时随地，畅享优质服务，就是这么任性！</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201602/02093023x5km.jpg\" /></p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192,80