 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">1、客户登陆手机支付宝账户，点击支付宝&ldquo;扫一扫&rdquo;，扫描活动二维码。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201512/18151552w4xg.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201512/18151611dmhi.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2、扫描成功后，进入生活缴费界面，输入客户名称、客户编号，点击下一步后，核对个人信息。输入购电金额后，点击充值。付款成功后，账单将自动抵扣立减金额。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201512/18151656xll4.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">活动中，如果您遇到任何问题，可拨打95598供电服务热线或支付宝客服电话95188进行咨询。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">除此之外，您还可以关注&ldquo;国网北京电力&rdquo;微信公众号或者下载&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;APP软件进行购电，方便您的生活。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">小贴士：家中电表的客户编号如何查询？</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">家中电表的客户编号是一组10位数字的号码，客户在&ldquo;掌上电力&rdquo;手机APP、支付宝、微信购电费或查电费时，经常会使用这个编号，如果您不知道家中的客户编号时，可通过4种方法进行查询。</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 15.55px/27.77px \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px\">1、在您的电力营业厅购电发票上</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201512/18151758mj39.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><font color=\"#3e3e3e\" size=\"3\">2、在您的银行等代售电网点购电发票上</font></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201512/1815185112br.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><font color=\"#3e3e3e\" size=\"3\">3、在您家的《智能电能表客户用电登记表》上</font></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201512/18151935lnk8.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><font color=\"#3e3e3e\" size=\"3\">4、在您家的新版电卡右下方</font></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://121.199.25.136:8888/Jeedw/u/cms/www/201512/18152026gu3y.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '1', '1', '2015-12-11 13:43:51', '国网北京电力', '2015-12-11 13:43:51', '', '0', '1', '');
